{"word":"H4264 - מַחֲנֶה - machăneh - makh-an-eh' - Army","slug":"H4264","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַחֲנֶה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>machăneh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>makh-an-eh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Army"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D7;&#x05E0;&#x05D4; - macha&#x0306;neh</b> - <i>makh-an-eh'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2583\">H2583</a>; an <i>encampment</i> (of travellers or troops); hence an <i>army</i>, whether literally (of soldiers) or figuratively (of dancers, angels, cattle, locusts, stars; or even the sacred courts): - army, band, battle, camp, company, drove, host, tents."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2583\">H2583</a>, <a href=\"#/H2588\">H2588</a>, <a href=\"#/H2595\">H2595</a>, <a href=\"#/H4265\">H4265</a>, <a href=\"#/H4266\">H4266</a>, <a href=\"#/H8465\">H8465</a>, <a href=\"#/H8466\">H8466</a>, <a href=\"#/H8470\">H8470</a>"}]}